title: Russell Dickerson Performs His #1 Hits + Lunchbox Tries To Make The News! + The Loser Watches Bridgerton Game
itunes:title: Russell Dickerson Performs His #1 Hits + Lunchbox Tries To Make The News! + The Loser Watches Bridgerton Game
description:
Russell Dickerson stops by the studio to perform a few #1 songs and talk about the time he met another famous Russell. Lunchbox was inspired by Darius Rucker going to a restaurant and paying for everyone’s meal so he tried to do the same thing! Bobby makes the show play a game and the loser has to watch Bridgerton (Netflix) as punishment! Plus, it's Fun Fact Friday...Amy teaches us something crazy about Garth Brooks!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
